text:
I am using HubSpot default Language Switcher. Does anyone have an idea on how to implement JS to have current language displayed instead of 'Language'? Also, how can I change the text from English - United States to just 'English'?

I used CSS
.lang_switcher_class:after {
   content: 'Language';
}
<#CGVAY1VQU|multi-language> <#CBA9UA4EN|javascript> <#C2YH119N2|hubl>
